cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a method based on artificial neural networks for the analysis of transmission electron microscopy images, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of lifelike synthesis of training data also suggests the involvement of image generation (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the utilization of artificial neural networks indicates the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
